chemo_detail:
Had 08 cycles of Inj. Doxorubicin+ Cyclophosphamide+ Carboplatin + Docetaxel based CT
up to 23.12.2021 (@BSMMU)> Surgey> Now 2nd line chemotherapy with Pacli-Carbo-Trastuzumab on
16/03/22 at India. Cycle 6 completed on 29.06.2022.
Maintenance therapy with Trastuzumab started on 20.07.2022 in India. M32 was due on 20.02.2024
